description.en: TUBE2 are produced from liquidity mining, there is no pre-mining nor private placement. Each block of TUBE2 will be proportionally given to the liquidity provider for market promotion, application, development and operation. TUBE2, as an autonomous token of a decentralized exchange, is used in DEX autonomous community voting and proposals in addition to the incentive liquidity scheme. In the autonomous community, in order to further promote the development of the TUBE2 ecology, nodes are also set. The purpose of setting the nodes is to promote ecological construction around the world, to ensure that the ecosystem continues to expand and develop and achieve balance and healthy data. Holding TUBE2 becomes an important condition for the node operation. The total output including TUBE2 will also be voted on by the autonomous community.
